title: [Medicine] New antibiotic that could treat drug-resistant infections and superbugs discovered

[Health] Study shows association between better neighborhood conditions and asthma rates: Children born in high-opportunity neighborhoods had an asthma incidence rate of 23.3 cases per 1,000 children, while those born in very low and low-opportunity neighborhoods had rates of 35.3 per 1,000 and 27 per 1,000
